'''Dave''' is a friend of [[Stewart Tyler]].

==History==
Dave came to the hospital with his friend, Stewart, who had been stabbed in the head during a fight at a tailgate party. They were both drunk, so they took a cab to the hospital. They were eager to get out of the hospital in order to get to the basketball game. While the doctors were out of the room discussing what to do, Dave pulled the knife out himself. They stitched up Stewart's head and he left against medical advice. Jackson put the two of them in a cab.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
He is friends with [[Stewart Tyler]].
